<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="File not found on BurnLink. The link may be malformed or the file has already been downloaded." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
  <title>File Not Found - BurnLink</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1410 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.05);
      }
    }

    header {
      padding: 2rem 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15);
      z-index: 100;
      animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .header-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    nav a.active {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    nav a.active:after {
      width: 100% !important;
    }

    nav a:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover:after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    main {
      padding: 8rem 0;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .error-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
    }

    .error-code {
      font-size: 5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    div > a, a {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.4);
      margin: 0.5rem;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      min-height: 44px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      -webkit-appearance: none;
      -moz-appearance: none;
      appearance: none;
    }

    a:hover:not(:disabled) {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.6);
    }

    a:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #ffa500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.4);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.1);
      border-color: #ffa500;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15);
      padding: 4rem 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.5);
      animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease-out;
    }

    .footer-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-section h3 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .footer-section a {
      display: block;
      padding: 0;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: none;
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-section a:hover {
      color: #ffa500;
      transform: translateX(5px);
      background: none;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.1);
      padding-top: 2rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1410 100%);
      }

      .error-code {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      header {
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }

      .error-container {
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }

      div > a, a {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0.75rem 0;
        padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
        width: 100%;
      }

      main {
        padding: 4rem 0;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }

      .header-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        width: 100%;
      }

      nav a {
        margin-left: 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .footer-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">BurnLink</div>
        <nav>
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="error-container">
      <div class="error-code">404</div>
      <h1>File Not Found</h1>
      <p>The file was not found, the link may be malformed, or it has already been downloaded once.</p>
      <div>
        <a href="/">Share a New File</a>
        <a href="/about" class="secondary">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Product</h3>
          <a href="/">Share Files</a>
          <a href="/about">How It Works</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Resources</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Documentation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Developer</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joy Majumdar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 BurnLink. Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
